<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KA KHAMHTU KA THUP TUAH CH55</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw ka Khamhtu, keimah thup tuah, Na hmun thiang chungah, Khi khua
 chung sunparnak toi ah, Nangmah sinah ka ra.

[C1]
   Maw, ka Khamhtu Bawipa keimah kha ka thup; Ka dawtmi Khamhtu,
   Nangmah sinah ka ra.

[V2]
 Vancung a ceu khua tha chungah, Ka dawt hawikom he, Kan Bawi Jesuh
 velngeihnak in, Ton thannak a um lai.

[C2]
   Maw, ka Khamhtu Bawipa keimah kha ka thup; Ka dawtmi Khamhtu,
   Nangmah sinah ka ra.

[V3]
 Maw ka Khamhtu, keimah thup tuah, Na hmun thiang chungah, Tili cung
 vate a zuan bang, Nangmah sinah ka ra.

[C3]
   Maw, ka Khamhtu Bawipa keimah kha ka thup; Ka dawtmi Khamhtu,
   Nangmah sinah ka ra.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>55</hymn_number>
</song>